originalText.text:
Dr Delphin is great! I called him and went on that same day. He is affordable and fast. I had my lab results and my medical forms in a few days. He speaks many languages and is very knowledgeable. Definitely call him the day you want to come in to claim a spot on the line of clients for the day.
Wholeheartedly trust this doctor to only do tests that are medically necessary. He is kind and respectful. Highly recommend.

originalText.text:
Terrible experience, awful service and horrible Doctor. Besides his horrendous bed manner, he has no sympathy for his patients. We decided to go here because my aunt said he spoke Spanish and she had had care with him before. Let me inform you, that If you expect any privacy, FORGET ABOUT IT, everyone in there LITERALLY will know your business, they will know why you are there and what medication you are getting. Nonetheless this is not the worst part, besides being mistreated you will be also talked down to, and Unless you put him in his place like I did, he will show you no respect.

I do not recommend this Doctor and really hope I won’t have to ever see him again.
